dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'St_Croix_Addresses_2018.gdb'. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
